Hello

William Michael Krzyzkowski was born in Loudoun County Virginia during a rare blizzard on March 26, 1998. He lived in a house on North St (which is labelled Nort Street in google maps) for 13 years. At the end of elementry school his family got what was supposed to be a dog but turned out to be a cat in disguise, and named her Mushu, after the dragon in Mulan. His family then moved to Lucketts, which is as close as possible to hell, aka Maryland. During the first year of Highschool he decided to become Will, and has been called that eversince. He currently attends James Madison University where he is Majoring in Computer Science with a Minor in Math, and will graduate in December 2019.
